The world’s largest vaccination drive hits 100 crore doses administered. Made in India vaccines - constitute 99.9% of the doses

#VaccineCentury
A remarkable feat has been achieved in India’s vaccination drive.  Not only have we produced vaccines but we have also administered and given them to a bigger population than even some continents.

#VaccineCentury
The Modi Govt has been enabling vaccine research and production. From setting up the vaccine task force in April 2020 to setting up the National expert group on vaccine administration for COVID-19, India has come a long way.

#VaccineCentury
The Modi Govt has tapped into the Indian pharma sector’s capabilities to scale the vaccination programme. Not only is the world’s first DNA vaccine ZyCov-D under Phase-III trials, but the 2 indigenous mRNA vaccines are also under advanced trial stages.

#VaccineCentury
India’s vaccination process was executed with a plan to perfection. The healthcare workers, Govt, frontline workers and 1.35 billion people stood up to the challenge to tackle covid.
